summary: An ordinance discontinuing the Eminent Domain proceedings for the acquisition of land and other property in Government Lot 2, Section 10, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W. M. for park purposes, authorized by Ordinance No. 81269, King County Cause No. 452193; providing for the payment into court of all taxable costs therein; and repealing said Ordinance No. 81269.
committee: Finance and Parks and Public Grounds
